			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">Ok! This quest originates in Everfrost. Somewhere on the plains of Everfrost are 3 NPCs (And it's not the 3 barbarian guards with the dog). If you talk to the wizard he'll tell you about a Wheel which needs to be completed. If you continue to follow his key words, he'll give you a box (WARNING: This box is NOSAVE, which means if you log out with it, it goes *Poof*). He will also give you a book of clues of where the pieces are.<BR>
<BR>
Thas all I know for now. I don't want to ruin the quest for anyone, but most of the hints are pretty easy to guess.
